---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"

const APP_URL = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_APP_URL ?? "http://localhost:3001"
---

<Layout title="Neon Starter Kit" description="Boilerplate SaaS Cloudflare-first">
  <main class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl text-center space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Neon Starter Kit
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">
        Boilerplate SaaS multi-tenant. Do <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">git clone</code> ao primeiro deploy em menos de 1 dia.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href={APP_URL}
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Abrir App
        </a>
        <a
          href="/docs"
          class="px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
        >
          Documentação
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-8 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg text-left">
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Edge-first</div>
          Cloudflare Pages + Workers. Zero cold starts.
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg text-left">
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Multi-tenant</div>
          Organizations desde o dia 1. Sem refatoração depois.
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg text-left">
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Free tier</div>
          Todos os serviços têm free tier generoso para o MVP.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
